data.description: Rare 4 bedroom ranch in Castle Crest subdivision now available! Eat in kitchen showcases 42 inch cabinets and all appliances included. Large windows overlooking the backyard deck and spacious yard. Primary bedroom and bath with walk in closet. Full partially finished basement includes a rec room area, and an extra space that could be used as a 5th bedroom or office. Fresh neutral paint throughout. Located on the desirable north side of Waukegan.
